{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"393c41f4bb","title":"第一师范讲堂录","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c579285487","index":0,"year":1913,"month":11,"day":1,"articleId":"393c41f4bb"}],"tags":[{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui1","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1913-1943卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui1a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9f9cf8061a","type":"title","text":"第一师范讲堂录","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"393c41f4bb"},{"id":"f2b9d77883","type":"paragraph","text":"修身。人情多耽安佚而惮苦，懒惰为万恶之渊薮。人而懒惰，农则废其田畴，工则废其规矩，商贾则废其所鬻，士则废其所学，业即废矣，无以为生，而杀身亡家乃随之矣。因而懒惰，始则不进，继则退行，继则衰弱，终则灭亡，可畏哉！故曰懒惰万恶之渊薮也。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"393c41f4bb"},{"id":"4902a70822","type":"paragraph","text":"奋斗。夫以五千之卒，敌十万之军。策罢乏之兵，当新霸之马。如此欲图存而不亡，非奋斗不可。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"393c41f4bb"},{"id":"d8f91a5a7b","type":"paragraph","text":"朝气。少年须有朝气，否则暮气中之。暮气之来，乘疏懈之隙也。故曰怠隋者生之坟墓。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"393c41f4bb"}],"page":{"id":"4566f31097","publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"393c41f4bb","start":9,"end":9}}}},"__N_SSG":true}